{"tid":270911,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一件關於「因而」你未必記得嘅事","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T16:28:55.000Z","uid":75927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06fe746f37ebb9c058100896dd426bf7bf417068","tid":270911,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.wikiwand.com/zh-hk/%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wikiwand.com%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%258D%2593%25E7%25BE%25B2&d=Y5GMY9%2FVJpBehHhQiuB7rcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2954a09c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wikiwand.com/zh-hk/%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">感情生活<br />\n吳卓羲的感情生活經常受到關注，在2005年《兒歌金曲頒獎典禮》中被鄭欣宜獻上一吻，結果廣管局接獲多宗投訴，而網友則譏諷那一吻為「死亡之吻」。</span>"},{"pid":"5d6138be88a3406f9e81ed61a3596452c24a4100","tid":270911,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa056af6443dcfdca357b9b7c238cdf8518a7ed5","tid":270911,"uid":80066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"不如我地"},{"pid":"67bbbcd465995288f338d5e8749f0961de7c0e0e","tid":270911,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d18e81d2e73e2ced6142e3df8dbd0048708422db","tid":270911,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23e8ef00e4603830489fa9464f6688676fad60b7","tid":270911,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28424bf9a5d11e8993e0b32fc22edfe23bfefd80","tid":270911,"uid":66997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T01:41:47.000Z","msg":"你到底有幾鍾意佢？"},{"pid":"b9f74f158201ab1a3287a5ac20eedbe9b2d52946","tid":270911,"uid":75927,"l